{
  "id": "RAW_41852a",
  "title": "OpenAI 顶级研究员：提示词工程已死",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mjc1NjM3MjY2MA==&mid=2691559295&idx=2&sn=c677d2fa447317fac4193e01a8a06b76",
  "date": "2025-07-15 10:13:00",
  "author": "腾讯科技",
  "siteName": "腾讯科技",
  "content": "\n \n \n  <p><br></p>\n  <h3 style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 0pt 24px;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"544075640\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.515625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"960\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"298\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=496855d0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fow6przZuPIHnZUjhov3Ddz0Z4kziaEb7MA0icJY3OCtcVX3kaMyTzjELbO7MQl8kgZLy3b1iakxCl7MmAqms6PNog%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5px;line-height: 1.75em;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;font-size: 18px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">目前，硅谷正经历一场关于AI开发范式的激烈辩论。继AI大神安德烈・卡帕西（Andrej Karpathy）力推“上下文工程”（context engineering）、宣告提示词工程（prompt engineering）过时之后，OpenAI顶级对齐研究员肖恩・格罗夫（Sean Grove）也</span></span><strong style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-weight: bolder;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">提出了相同的观点：提示词工程确实过时了</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，但他指出了新的观点：未来应当属于“规范化编程”（spec-writing）。</span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5px;line-height: 1.75em;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;font-size: 18px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">规范化编程（spec-writing）是一个涉及编写、定义和记录系统需求、功能、行为规范的过程，其目的是确保开发团队、利益相关方和机器能够清楚地理解系统的目标和方向。</span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5px;line-height: 1.75em;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;font-size: 18px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">作为OpenAI核心研究团队的重要成员，格罗夫在人工智能安全和模型对齐领域造诣深厚。他</span></span><strong style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-weight: bolder;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">目前正组建OpenAI新的智能体鲁棒性团队</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，直接参与通用人工智能的安全演化工作。在近日的一次技术演讲中，这位业界专家提出了与卡帕西不同的发展方向。</span></span></span></p></h3>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"544058943\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.1270815074496056\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1141\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"73\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=09e5945c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fow6przZuPIFNmictFHYdncDXcq2icHxwTK56dgibfgrWYob2quE8oGtLxx75S8uw6wlJmuVUo870E4Ya3DraUcZaQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 0pt 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-weight: bold;font-style: normal;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0pt;vertical-align: baseline;\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 20px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(23, 91, 190);\">两条路径，一个共识：提示词工程的末日</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-weight: bold;font-style: normal;color: rgb(26, 26, 26);letter-spacing: 0pt;vertical-align: baseline;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"544075641\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5395833333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"960\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"312\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8cc174c5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fow6przZuPIHnZUjhov3Ddz0Z4kziaEb7MDia57KdH9NdqsVWK9UibqU1f9WBibaqDTQzVkHcfUWJ0VWEgfgtLG43uQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">格罗夫阐述规范化编程的优点</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5px;line-height: 1.75em;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;font-size: 18px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">当前正值AI智能体的爆发期，OpenAI总裁格雷格・布罗克曼（Greg Brockman）多次表示 “2025年是AI智能体的元年”。在此背景下，传统的提示词工程因“一次性”和缺乏系统性的缺陷，已被广泛认为走到了尽头。卡帕西与格罗夫两位专家对此达成共识，但提出了截然不同的解决方案：</span></span><strong style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-weight: bolder;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">卡帕西的上下文工程与格罗夫的规范化编程，分别代表了“输入优化”与“意图澄清”两种路径</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5px;line-height: 1.75em;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;font-size: 18px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">卡帕西将上下文工程称为“一门精深的科学，也是一门巧妙的艺术”，认为它是工业级大语言模型应用的正确方向。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5px;line-height: 1.75em;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;font-size: 18px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">他指出：“大多数AI智能体的失败，不是模型能力的不足，而是上下文的失败。” 其核心在于“在恰当时机、以恰当格式提供恰当信息”，涵盖指令、用户输入、状态历史、长期记忆、检索信息、可用工具和结构化输出等全方位信息。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5px;line-height: 1.75em;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;font-size: 18px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-weight: bolder;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">卡帕西强调“长期记忆”的重要性，主张通过动态管理历史交互数据确保模型行为符合预期</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。他认为未来程序员需成为“信息架构师”，并批评将工业级应用简单视为“ChatGPT套壳”的观点。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5px;line-height: 1.75em;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;font-size: 18px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">格罗夫则提出更为激进的“规范化编程”理念，认为</span></span><strong style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-weight: bolder;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">提示词工程和上下文工程的共同缺陷是：人类花费大量精力优化与AI的交互，却从未真正说清自己想要什么。他主张通过结构化规范文档明确开发意图和价值判断，使其成为比代码更重要的“源代码”。</span></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5px;line-height: 1.75em;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;font-size: 18px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">“你以为你告诉了模型你想要什么，但后来你才发现，你从来没真正说清楚过——甚至你自己都不完全明白真正想要的是什么，”格罗夫说，“就像盖房子前只跟建筑师说‘我要一个漂亮的房子’，却没说清细节，最后抱怨‘这不是我想要的’，问题根源在自己没画好蓝图。” 他进一步解释：“提示词工程像教你礼貌沟通，上下文工程像整理建筑材料，但如果连‘要什么样的房子’都没搞懂，再礼貌的语气、再全的材料也建不出想要的家。”</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"544075642\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5489583333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"960\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"317\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=971e98d1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fow6przZuPIHnZUjhov3Ddz0Z4kziaEb7M1k6GXVYE9PWvTvMhzX1vFgoWCibBTyIVvndnyrxOCbFtJV8miablPqXw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">代码只占工作价值的10%到20%，另外80%到90%体现在结构化沟通中</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">格罗夫强调：“代码只占工作价值的10%到20%，另外80%到90%体现在结构化沟通中。规范是人类的指南针，确保每一步都知道‘为什么要做这个’。” 他以OpenAI的Model Spec为例，这份开源Markdown文档用自然语言表达模型的价值观和行为准则，可通过“审慎对齐”（deliberative alignment）技术嵌入模型训练，使意图成为模型的“内在记忆”。格罗夫将规范比喻为“源码”，认为代码只是其“有损投影”，并设想未来IDE将转变为“集成意图澄清器”，助力意图澄清与协作。</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-weight: normal;font-style: normal;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0pt;vertical-align: baseline;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"544058942\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.1270815074496056\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1141\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"73\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a788a5c3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fow6przZuPIFNmictFHYdncDXcq2icHxwTKJ3b7BPnws25UBZG6CpXBwibolsUE4eOQbzec7e2vNkjtdGXDLgkO1mA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 0pt 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-weight: bold;font-style: normal;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0pt;vertical-align: baseline;\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 20px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(23, 91, 190);\">两种方法的本质区别</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-weight: bold;font-style: normal;color: rgb(26, 26, 26);letter-spacing: 0pt;vertical-align: baseline;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5px;line-height: 1.75em;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;font-size: 18px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">总结来说，两位专家虽然都反对传统提示词工程，但解决方案思路迥异：</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5px;line-height: 1.75em;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;font-size: 18px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">卡帕西的上下文工程专注于“如何更好地与AI沟通”，认为智能体失败源于“上下文的失败”——无法在恰当时机、以恰当格式提供恰当信息。其核心是</span></span><strong style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-weight: bolder;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">系统化收集、组织和传递信息，通过优化输入提升AI表现</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，强调 “长期记忆”对动态管理历史数据的作用。这是“输入优化”思路：假设目标明确，关键是高效传达。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5px;line-height: 1.75em;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;font-size: 18px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">格罗夫的“规范化编程”则聚焦“如何明确我们真正想要什么”，认为</span></span><strong style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-weight: bolder;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AI开发的问题源于人类对自身目标的模糊认知。</span></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"544075643\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5416666666666666\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"960\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"313\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4c670aa4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fow6przZuPIHnZUjhov3Ddz0Z4kziaEb7MC2KfMHCBRVvzNdLLhsB2FswyJaKUpgmol8diaSc5XMfKM9goHIVDvBA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">介绍OpenAI Model Spec</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">“粗糙演示与惊艳智能体的根本区别，在于是否明确成功的定义，”他说。其核心是通过</span></span><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-weight: bolder;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">结构化规范文档</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">（如 Model Spec）清晰表达意图和价值观，并利用“审慎对齐”技术将规范嵌入模型训练，使意图成为“内在记忆”。这是“意图澄清”思路：与AI沟通前，人类需先明确目标并以可版本化、可测试的形式记录。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5px;line-height: 1.75em;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;font-size: 18px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">简言之，</span></span><strong style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-weight: bolder;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">卡帕西关注“怎么做”（优化输入实现已知目标），格罗夫关注“做什么”（通过规范明确意图本身）。格罗夫指出：“规范是代码的‘源码’，代码只是其有损投影，真正价值在于清晰表达的意图</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。”</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5px;line-height: 1.75em;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;font-size: 18px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">尽管侧重点不同，两人都认同提示词工程的局限性，预见程序员角色向 “意图设计者” 转变：卡帕西要求程序员成为 “信息架构师”，格罗夫则认为未来稀缺技能是 “编写完整表达意图与价值的规范的能力”。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"73\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"544058941\" data-ratio=\"0.1270815074496056\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1141\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7a502c11&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fow6przZuPIFNmictFHYdncDXcq2icHxwTKEkoHuVs0tsCevYcBM7icLo1rxxzUqaNcmCXbADOyH1UIictDIYibbWv1A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 0pt 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-weight: bold;font-style: normal;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0pt;vertical-align: baseline;\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 20px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(23, 91, 190);\">OpenAI内部实践：</span></span></span></h3>\n  <h3 style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 0pt 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-weight: bold;font-style: normal;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0pt;vertical-align: baseline;\" data-font-family=\"微软雅黑\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 20px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(23, 91, 190);\">Model Spec的成功验证</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;font-weight: bold;font-style: normal;color: rgb(26, 26, 26);letter-spacing: 0pt;vertical-align: baseline;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"544075644\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5385416666666667\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"960\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"311\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2985e7f7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fow6przZuPIHnZUjhov3Ddz0Z4kziaEb7MxBERxLicuqboXClcTsdhjtpMeRn4noYorlG6U7yHejYEyjnHVmqLI3A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">格罗夫认为AI工程中一切都可以视为规格</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">格罗夫深度参与设计的OpenAI Model Spec（指其模型在API和ChatGPT中的行为方式，涵盖了模型行为的设计原则、规则和默认行为，并强调了根据人类反馈进行持续改进），是规范化编程的典型案例。开源的Model Spec以自然语言系统化表达了OpenAI对AI模型在价值观、行为准则和伦理约束方面的期望，为开发者、用户和AI系统提供透明参考框架。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5px;line-height: 1.75em;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;font-size: 18px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">格罗夫团队开发的“审慎对齐”技术，为规范化编程注入实践能力：将Model Spec 中的规范直接转化为模型训练和评估的约束条件，通过“规范驱动微调”将抽象意图和价值观“编码”进模型参数，显著提升运行效率和行为稳定性。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5px;line-height: 1.75em;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;font-size: 18px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">“传统对齐依赖大量数据标注和后期修正，效率低且难保证一致性，” 格罗夫解释，“通过审慎对齐，规范成为训练原材料，让每条准则都被翻译成模型可理解的优化目标，使对齐更可控，行为更可预测。” 他举例：Model Spec中的准则，例如“面对敏感问题保持中立尊重”，通过该技术转化为可量化损失函数嵌入训练，模型生成回答时会主动避免偏见，无需额外后处理。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5px;line-height: 1.75em;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;font-size: 18px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这项突破为规范化编程提供实证支持。格罗夫强调，其核心是“从混乱到秩序”，通过结构化表达人类意图并应用于AI开发，既提高效率，又为伦理治理提供新可能。“未来，所有AI系统或能基于通用、公开的规范标准开发评估，这将极大增强AI的可信度和透明度。”</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5px;line-height: 1.75em;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;font-size: 18px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">尽管两位专家的路径不同，但都捕捉到时代转折点。犹如格罗夫说：“我们正在见证一个新时代的开始，我们的目标是让人类与AI协作更高效、安全。我和卡帕西的观点没有对错之分，而是一场共同的探索”。</span></span><strong style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-weight: bolder;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">（文/腾讯科技特约编译 无忌 编辑/海伦）</span></span></strong></span></p>\n \n",
  "aiSummary": "OpenAI 顶级研究员肖恩·格罗夫提出“规范化编程”取代提示词工程，强调通过明确意图而非优化输入来构建 AI 智能体。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "OpenAI 顶级研究员肖恩·格罗夫提出“规范化编程”取代提示词工程，强调通过明确意图而非优化输入来构建 AI 智能体。",
  "summary": "文章深入探讨了 AI 开发范式的演变，指出传统提示词工程已过时。继安德烈·卡帕西提出“上下文工程”后，OpenAI 顶级研究员肖恩·格罗夫提出了更激进的“规范化编程”理念。两位专家虽路径不同，但都认为 AI 智能体失败的根源在于人类未能清晰表达自身意图。卡帕西的“上下文工程”侧重于系统化收集、组织和传递信息，优化输入以提升 AI 表现，强调“信息架构师”的角色。而格罗夫的“规范化编程”则聚焦于通过结构化规范文档（如 OpenAI 的 Model Spec）明确开发意图和价值观，并利用“审慎对齐”技术将其嵌入模型训练，使意图成为模型的“内在记忆”。文章通过对比两种方法，强调了“意图澄清”的重要性，并指出未来程序员将向“意图设计者”转变。OpenAI Model Spec 的成功实践为“规范化编程”提供了实证支持，预示着 AI 开发将走向更高效、可控和透明的未来。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "提示词工程已过时，AI 开发范式正向更高级别演进。",
      "explanation": "传统提示词工程因一次性和缺乏系统性，无法适应 AI 智能体爆发期复杂需求，亟需更系统、更明确的开发范式。"
    },
    {
      "point": "“上下文工程”侧重优化输入，通过系统化信息传递提升 AI 表现。",
      "explanation": "卡帕西强调在恰当时机提供恰当信息，涵盖指令、记忆、工具等，将程序员变为“信息架构师”，以解决 AI 的“上下文失败”问题。"
    },
    {
      "point": "“规范化编程”聚焦意图澄清，通过结构化规范明确人类目标。",
      "explanation": "格罗夫认为人类常不清楚自己真正想要什么，主张将清晰的意图和价值观写入规范文档，并通过“审慎对齐”嵌入模型，使意图成为 AI 的“内在记忆”。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "提示词工程确实过时了，但他指出了新的观点：未来应当属于\"规范化编程\"（spec-writing）。",
    "大多数 AI 智能体的失败，不是模型能力的不足，而是上下文的失败。",
    "你以为你告诉了模型你想要什么，但后来你才发现，你从来没真正说清楚过------甚至你自己都不完全明白真正想要的是什么。",
    "代码只占工作价值的 10%到 20%，另外 80%到 90%体现在结构化沟通中。规范是人类的指南针，确保每一步都知道'为什么要做这个'。",
    "我和卡帕西的观点没有对错之分，而是一场共同的探索。"
  ],
